# Admin seed (HasData — giống RoleSeed)

- `Model/Data/Seed/AppUserSeed.cs` — `GetUsers()` trả `AppUser[]` (Id=1, admin@gmail.com, 12345).
- `AppDbContext.OnModelCreating` → `modelBuilder.Entity<AppUser>().HasData(AppUserSeed.GetUsers())`.
- Migration: `dotnet ef migrations add` → `InsertData` khi `database update`.
- **Không** seed Admin runtime qua Service/JSON/SQL thô.
